<div class="arch-wrap">
    <h1>🏛️ MakauTech — System Architecture</h1>
    <p class="arch-sub">
        Database design, OOP concepts, and code patterns used in the project.
        Built on ASP.NET Core 8 MVC + Entity Framework Core 8 + MySQL (Pomelo).
    </p>

    <div class="arch-toc">
        <strong>Jump to:</strong>
        <a href="#erd">ERD</a>
        <a href="#pk">Primary Keys</a>
        <a href="#fk">Foreign Keys</a>
